{"tid":2153952,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"議會延任一年，選管會必須立即為港島新界東懸空議席作出補選工作","createTime":"2020-08-13T00:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T13:47:25.000Z","uid":9348,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c854902cd1ace05ebae104ef6f93b3aa4a7936f6","tid":2153952,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T00:40:35.000Z","msg":"...基於實際考慮因素，立法會香港島地方選區及新界東地方選區兩個議席空缺的補選籌備工作預計需時超過六個月。由於《立法會條例》規定，填補立法會議席空缺的補選，不得在立法會<span class=\"red\">現屆任期結束前的四個月內舉行</span>，故此，選管會未能就上述地方選區的兩個議席空缺安排補選...<br />\n<br />\n...《立法會條例》第36（1）（a）條提到，選管會須在立法會秘書根據第35條宣布立法會議席出現空缺時，安排舉行一項補選，惟《立法會條例》第36（2）條亦同時列明，舉行立法會補選以填補議席空缺的期限為現屆立法會任期結束前的四個月，即今年五月三十一日或之前...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泛民豬，呢個回力鏢先係你哋嘅籌碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37024d8c74d58f65901737c458687771665e263","tid":2153952,"uid":51271,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T00:41:12.000Z","msg":"係喎，要補選"},{"pid":"d69a25992bfeafb2c8ff04a0bf00f2df426a4528","tid":2153952,"uid":150427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T00:42:21.000Z","msg":"係?"},{"pid":"8a54c782a6ab986155b8c81315de8d72e50d90c5","tid":2153952,"uid":49016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T00:42:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d0e1ea9f8df241dc311d225cc0c9c3600ad8c4a","tid":2153952,"uid":156913,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T00:50:47.000Z","msg":"好呀<br />\n要留就推呢個<br />\n總之煩到支共已經有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7701a92703c8d0ca94e4265d862720cbf711e6e","tid":2153952,"uid":358691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T00:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eaeaa92228500e2008b0ec59e0b1b5a4db1ec10","tid":2153952,"uid":221051,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime